  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] You may play 1 red Tamer card with a play cost of
    4 or less from your hand without paying the cost. Then, if you have a Tamer with
    [Sora Takenouchi] in its name, return 1 red Digimon card from your trash to the
    hand.'
